><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>&#215;</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>가", "type": 0}, {"text": " 성립합니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;예를 들어,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 다음 그림과 같이", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98644_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>90</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>인", "type": 0}, {"text": " 직각삼각형 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>의", "type": 0}, {"text": " 꼭짓점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi></math>에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>에 내린 수선의 발을", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98648_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>H</mi></math>라고 합니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi></math>,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98650_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi></math>일 때,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98651_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>x</mi></math>의 값의 값을 구해 봅시다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98652_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br> <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><msup><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo></math><math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>&#215;</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>이므로", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3472}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><msup><mn>6</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>&#215;</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></math>,", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>36</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi></math>,", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>27</mn></math>,", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn></math>입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": " 따라서 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>x</mi></math>의 값은", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>9</mn></math>입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "[문단 나누기]", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>접은 도형에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " 닮음 조건을 응용하여", "type": 0}, {"text": " 닮음인 삼각형을", "type": 0}, {"text": " 어떻게 찾을까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br> (1) 다음 그림과 같이", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98665_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 직사각형 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>D</mi></math>에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>E</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>를 접는 선으로 하여", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98667_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 꼭짓점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>B</mi></math>가", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>위의", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98669_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, 