	(206, 616, '[{"text": " 삼각형에서 평행선을 그을 때", "type": 0}, {"text": " 선분의 길이의 비는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 어떻게 될까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;삼각형의 한 변에", "type": 0}, {"text": " 평행한 직선을", "type": 0}, {"text": " 그었을 때 생기는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 선분의 길이의 비에 대하여", "type": 0}, {"text": " 알아봅시다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " 한 직선이", "type": 0}, {"text": " 두 변 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></math> 또는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 그 연장선과 만나는 점을", "type": 0}, {"text": " 각각 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>D</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>E</mi></math>라고 할 때,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 다음이 성립합니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;(1) <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></menclose><mo>&#11005;</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi></menclose></math>이면", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></menclose><mo>=</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>E</mi></menclose><mo>=</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi></menclose></math>입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;(증명) 다음 그림과 같이", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98024_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 변 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>에 평행한 직선을 그어", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98025_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 두 변 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></math> 또는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 그 연장선과 만나는 점을", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98027_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 각각 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>D</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>E</mi></math>라고 하면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98028_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>와 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi></math>에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></menclose><mo>&#11005;</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi></menclose></math>이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98030_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi></math>,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98031_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>E</mi><mi>D</mi></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98032_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 즉,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 두 쌍의 대응각의 크기가", "type": 0}, {"text": " 각각 같으므로", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>&#8765;</mo><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi></math>(<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>A</mi></math> 닮음)입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98036_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 따라서", "type": 0}, {"text": " 닮음인 두 삼각형의", "type": 0}, {"text": " 대응하는 변의", "type": 0}, {"text": " 길이의 비가 같으므로", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3473}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></menclose><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98041_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>E</mi></menclose><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98042_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi></menclose></math>가", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98043_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 성립합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98044_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;(2) <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></menclose><mo>&#11005;</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi></menclose></math>이면", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>D</mi><mi>B</mi></menclose><mo>=</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>E</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>E</mi><mi>C</mi></menclose></math