\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>D</mi><mi>C</mi></menclose></math>와 평행한", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98172_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 선분 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>Q</mi></menclose></math>를 긋습니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98173_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9633;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>Q</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>D</mi></math>는 평행사변형이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98174_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>P</mi><mi>F</mi></menclose><mo>=</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></menclose><mo>=</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>Q</mi><mi>C</mi></menclose><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi></math>이고,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98175_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>Q</mi></math>에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98176_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>E</mi><mi>P</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>B</mi><mi>Q</mi></menclose><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98177_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>m</mi><mo>:</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>)</mo></math>,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98178_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "  <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<menclose notation=\\"top\\">&#160;<mi>E</mi> <mi>P</mi>&#160;</menclose> <mo>=</mo> <mfrac>&#160;<mrow>&#160;<mi>m</mi> <mo>(</mo> <mi>b</mi> <mo>-</mo