h/MathML\\"><mi>a</mi><mo>:</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98214_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>E</mi><mi>F</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><mi>b</mi></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98215_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;따라서", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>E</mi><mi>F</mi></menclose><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98217_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 또한", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>D</mi></math>에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>B</mi><mi>F</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>F</mi><mi>C</mi></menclose><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98220_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>B</mi><mi>E</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>E</mi><mi>D</mi></menclose><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98221_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>a</mi><mo>:</mo><mi>b</mi></math>가", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98222_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 성립합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98223_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "[문단 나누기]", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>삼각형의", "type": 0}, {"text": " 내각과 외각의 이등분선에는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 어떤 성질이 있을까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;삼각형에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " 한 내각과 외각에", "type": 0}, {"text": " 이등분선을 그으면", "type": 0}, {"text": " 두 개의 삼각형이 생기고,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 다음과 같은", "type": 0}, {"text": " 선분의 길이의 비가", "type": 0}, {"text": " 성립합니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br> (1) <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98235_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></menclose></math>가 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi></math>의 이등분선이면,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98236_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></menclose><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98237_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>B</mi><mi>D</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>C</mi><mi>D</mi></menclose></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98238_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br> (증명) 다음 그림과 같이", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98239_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>C</mi></math>를 지나고", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98240_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></menclose></math>에 평행한 직선이", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98241_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>B</mi><mi>A</mi></menclose></math>의 연장선과 만나는 점을", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98242_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>E</mi></math>라고 하면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98243_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>E</mi></math>에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98244_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></menclose><mo>&#11005;</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>E</mi><mi>C</mi></menclose></math>이므로", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>E</mi></menclose><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98246_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>B</mi><mi>D</mi></menclose><mo>:</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>C</mi><mi>D</mi></menclose></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98247_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;또,", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></menclose><mo>&#11005;</mo><menclose notation=\\"top\\"><mi>E</mi><mi>C</mi></menclose></math>이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/98249_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>B</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>E</mi><mi>C</mi></math>(동위각),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_im