"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>N</mi><mi>D</mi></math>와 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>E</mi><mi>N</mi><mi>C</mi></math>에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/99760_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>N</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>N</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/99761_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>N</mi><mi>D</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>E</mi><mi>N</mi><mi>C</mi></math>(맞꼭지각),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/99762_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi><mi>N</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>E</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>N</mi></math>(엇각)이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/99763_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>N</mi><mi>D</mi><mo>&#8801;</mo><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>E</mi><mi>N</mi><mi>C</mi></math>(<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>S</mi><mi>A</mi></math> 합동)입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/99764_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 따라서 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>N</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>E</mi><mi>N</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>입니다.", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3477}}, {"text": "<br> <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>E</mi></math>에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/99766_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": 