ath/MathML\\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>8</mn></mfrac><mi>&#960;</mi><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></math>입니다.", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3491}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;따라서", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>가", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/101249_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 성립합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/101250_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "[문단 나누기]", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;(5) 다음 그림과 같이", "type": 0}, {"text": " 직각삼각형 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>의", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/101253_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 세 변을 지름으로 하는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 세 반원에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/101255_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=\\"normal\\">&#49353;</mi><mo>&#52832;</mo><mo>&#54620;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>&#48512;&#48516;&#51032;</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>&#45331;&#51060;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/101256_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/101257_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>b</mi><mi>c</mi></math>가 성립합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/101258_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;(증명)", "type": 0}, {"tex