>&#44060;&#51032;</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#54637;</mo><mo>)</mo></math>으로 묶어", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math> 꼴로 만들어", "type": 0}, {"text": " 인수분해합니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;예를 들어,", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>c</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mi>c</mi><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>을", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108328_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 인수분해하여 봅시다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br> 공통인수가 생기도록", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108330_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>2</mn></math>개의 항씩 묶어 보면", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>c</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mi>c</mi><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108332_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>a</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>-</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>)</mo></math>이고,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108333_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 공통인수로 묶으면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108334_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>)</mo></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108335_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 따라서", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>a<