text": " 이차방정식", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>10</mn></math>을", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105317_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 풀어 봅시다.", "type": 0}, {"text": " <br>&nbsp;먼저 이차방정식의 모든 항을", "type": 0}, {"text": " 좌변으로 이항하여 정리하면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105320_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>이고,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105321_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 좌변을 인수분해하면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105322_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105323_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>의 성질을 이용하면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105324_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105325_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 또는 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105326_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 이차방정식의 해는", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105327_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w