type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105856_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br> ①", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105857_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 늘어난 가로의 길이를", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105858_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>x</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi></math>라고 합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105859_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<br> ②", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105860_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 가로, 세로의 길이를", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105861_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 똑같이 늘였더니", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105862_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 넓이가", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105863_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 처음의 직사각형의 넓이의", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>2</mn></math>배가 되므로", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3566}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mn>12</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&#215;</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>12</mn><mo>&#215;</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo></math>인", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105866_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 방정식이 성립합니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br> ③ 이 방정식을 풀면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105868_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>96</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>20</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>192</mn></math>,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/105869_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/