998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>sin</mi><mi>B</mi></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/107928_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 또", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>180</mn><mo>&#176;</mo><mo>-</mo><mo>(</mo><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>+</mo><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>B</mi><mo>)</mo></math>이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/107930_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>H</mi></math>에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/107931_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mi>sin</mi><mi>C</mi></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/107932_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 따라서", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>sin</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mi>sin</mi><mi>C</mi></math>이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/107934_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>c</mi><mi>sin</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/107935_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;이번에는", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mro