ath>이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/107946_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>c</mi><mi>sin</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/107947_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;예를 들어,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 다음 그림과 같은 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/107949_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>x</mi></math>의 길이를 구해봅시다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/107950_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;꼭짓점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi></math>에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>에 내린 수선의 발을", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>D</mi></math>라고 하면", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>D</mi></math>에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mi>sin</mi><mn>45</mn><mo>&#176;</mo><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3607}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>6</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mo>&#215;</mo><mfrac><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></math>이고,", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></move