h xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>M</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>N</mi></math>이라 하고", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108743_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>M</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>N</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108744_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>B</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>60</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>일 때,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108745_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>x</mi></math>의 크기를 구해봅시다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108746_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>M</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>N</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>이면", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원의 중심과 현의 관계에 의해", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>이므로", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>는 이등변삼각형입니다.", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3615}}, {"text": " 따라서", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>(</mo><mn>180</mn><mo>&#176;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>60</mn><mo>&#176;</mo><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>60</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;이상을 정리하면", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원의 중심과", "type": 0}, {"text": " 현의 길이 사이에는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 다음과 같은 관계가 있습니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br> (1) 원의 중심으로부터", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108758_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 같은 거리에 있는", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108759_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 두 현의 길이는 같다.", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3616}}, {"text": " 즉,", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>M</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>N</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>이면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108762_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>이다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108763_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;(2) 길이가 같은 두 현은", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원의 중심으로부터", "type": 0}, {"text": " 같은 거리에 있다.", "type": 0}, {"text": " 즉,", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>이면", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>M</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>N</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>이다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108769_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>", "type": 0}]', NULL, NULL, '2024-02-15 09:58:33', '2024-02-15 09:58:33'),
	(244, 730, '[{"text": "원의 접선에는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 어떤 성질이 있을까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br> 직선 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>l</mi></math>이", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108464_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>와", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108465_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 한 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>T</mi></math>에서 만날 때,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108466_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 직선 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>l</mi></math>은", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>에 접한다고 하고,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 이 직선 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>l</mi></math>을", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>의 접선,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108470_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>T</mi></math>를", "type": 0}, {"text": " 접점이라 합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108472_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;이때,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 반지름 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi><mi>T</mi></math>는", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108474_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 원의 중심 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>와", "type": 0}, {"text": " 직선 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>l</mi></math>을 잇는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 가장 짧은 선분이고", "type": 0}, {"text": " 직선 밖의 한 점에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " 직선에 그은 선분 중에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " 가장 짧은 것은", "type": 0}, {"text": " 그 직선의 수선이므로", "type": 0}, {"text": " 반지름 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi><mi>T</mi></math>는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 직선 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>l</mi></math>에 수직입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108483_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 즉,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 직선 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>l</mi></math>이 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>의 접선이면", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>T</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>&#8869;</mo><mi>l</mi></math>가 성립합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108486_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br> 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math> 밖의 한 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>P</mi></math>에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108487_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>에 그을 수 있는 접선은", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>2</mn></math>개입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108489_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 두 접선의 접점을", "type": 0}, {"text": " 각각 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>B</mi></math>라고 할 때,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108491_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 두 선분 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi></math>와 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi></math>의 길이를", "type": 0}, {"text": " 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>P</mi></math>에서 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>에 그은", "type": 0}, {"text": " &lsquo;접선의 길이&rsquo;라고 합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108494_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 이때", "type": 0}, {"text": " 두 선분 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi></math>와 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi></math>의 길이는", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108496_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 같습니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108497_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;이와 같은 성질이", "type": 0}, {"text": " 항상 성립함을 알아봅시다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;다음 그림과 같이", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math> 밖의 한 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>P</mi></math>에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108501_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 이 원에 그은 두 접선의 접점을", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108502_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>B</mi></math>라고 할 때,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108503_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>O</mi></math>와 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>O</mi></math>에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108504_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>O</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>O</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>90</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108505_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>는 공통,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108506_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>(반지름)이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108507_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>O</mi><mo>&#8801;</mo><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>O</mi></math>(<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>R</mi><mi>H</mi><mi>S</mi></math> 합동)입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108508_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 따라서", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108510_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 즉,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원 밖의 한 점에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108512_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 그 원에 그은 두 접선의 길이는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 같습니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108514_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;이상을 정리하면,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원의 외부의 한 점에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108516_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 원에 그은 두 접선의 길이는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 서로 같습니다.", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3617}}, {"text": " 즉,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108519_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>가 항상 성립합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108520_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;예를 들어,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 다음 그림에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108522_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>는 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>의 접선이고", "type": 0}, {"text": " 두 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>B</mi></math>는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 각각 그 접점일 때,", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>의 길이를 구해봅시다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108526_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>(</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi><mo>)</mo></math>이고", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>O</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>90</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>이므로", "type": 0}, {"text": " 직각삼각형 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>O</mi></math>에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " 피타고라스 정리에 의해", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msup><mn>13</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><msup><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><msqrt><mn>144</mn></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn><mo>(</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi><mo>)</mo></math>입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;한편,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math> 밖의 한 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>P</mi></math>에 대하여", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108534_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>는 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>의 접선이고", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108535_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 두 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>B</mi></math>는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 각각 그 접점일 때,", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9633;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>O</mi></math>의 내각의 크기의 합은", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108538_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>360</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>이고", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3618}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>O</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>O</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>90</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108540_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>+</mo><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>O</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>180</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>가 성립합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108541_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "[문단 나누기]", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>원의 접선의 길이를", "type": 0}, {"text": " 활용해 볼까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br> (1) 다음 그림과 같이", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108545_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 세 직선 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>E</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>가", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108546_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>의 접선이고", "type": 0}, {"text": " 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>D</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>E</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>F</mi></math>는 접점일 때,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108548_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>의 둘레의 길이는", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108549_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi></math>에서 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>에 그은", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108550_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 두 접선의 길이의", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108551_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 합과", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108552_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 같습니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108553_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;이를", "type": 0}, {"text": " 접선의 성질을 이용해", "type": 0}, {"text": " 확인해 봅시다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108556_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<br> 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>B</mi></math>에서 그은 접선에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108557_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>F</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>이고,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108558_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>C</mi></math>에서 그은 접선에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108559_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>F</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>입니다.", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3619}}, {"text": " 이때", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108561_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>의 둘레의 길이는", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mi mathvariant=\\"normal\\">&#51032;</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>&#46168;&#47112;&#51032;</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>&#44600;&#51060;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108563_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>F</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>F</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108564_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108565_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108566_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108567_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>2</mn><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108568_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<br> (2) 다음 그림과 같이", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108569_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 반원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math> 위의", "type": 0}, {"text": " 한 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>E</mi></math>에서 그은 접선이", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108571_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 지름 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>의", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108572_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 양 끝점에서 그은 접선과", "type": 0}, {"text": " 만나는 점을", "type": 0}, {"text": " 각각 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>D</mi></math>라고 하면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108575_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 원의 접선의 길이를 이용하여", "type": 0}, {"text": " 반원의 지름의 길이를", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108577_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 구할 수 있습니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108578_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br> 이를", "type": 0}, {"text": " 접선의 성질을 이용해", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108580_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 확인해 봅시다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br> <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108582_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108583_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108584_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108585_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 또한", "type": 0}, {"text": " 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi></math>에서 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>에 내린", "type": 0}, {"text": " 수선의 발을 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>H</mi></math>라고 하면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108588_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>-</mo><mover><mrow><mi>H</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>-</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>이고,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108589_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>H</mi><mi>D</mi></math>는 직각삼각형이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108590_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 피타고라스 정리를 이용하면", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mi>&#48152;&#50896;&#51032;</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>&#51648;&#47492;&#51032;</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>&#44600;&#51060;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108592_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108593_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><msqrt><msup><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><msup><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108594_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<br>", "type": 0}]', NULL, NULL, '2024-02-15 09:58:33', '2024-02-15 09:58:33'),
	(245, 733, '[{"text": "삼각형의 내접원에는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 어떤 성질이 있을까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;삼각형의 내접원에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원의 접선의 성질을 이용하면", "type": 0}, {"text": " 이 삼각형의 둘레의", "type": 0}, {"text": " 길이와 넓이를", "type": 0}, {"text": " 구할 수 있습니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br> 다음 그림과 같이", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108778_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>가", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108779_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>의 내접원이고,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 세 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>D</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>E</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>F</mi></math>가", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108781_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 그 접점일 때,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 접선의 성질에 의해", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108784_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>F</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108785_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108786_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>F</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108787_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>F</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108788_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>,</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108789_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>F</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mi>z</mi></math>라고 하면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108790_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mi mathvariant=\\"normal\\">&#51032;</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>&#46168;&#47112;&#51032;</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>&#44600;&#51060;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108791_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108792_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>z</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>z</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108793_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>2</mn><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>z</mi><mo>)</mo></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108794_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;또 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>의 반지름의 길이를", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>r</mi></math>이라 하면,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108796_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>A</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></math>의", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108797_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 밑변의 길이가", "type": 0}, {"text": " 각각 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>a</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>c</mi></math>이고,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108799_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 높이가 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>r</mi></math>이므로", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3620}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mi mathvariant=\\"normal\\">&#51032;</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>&#45331;&#51060;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108801_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>+</mo><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>A</mi><mo>+</mo><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108802_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>a</mi><mi>r</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>b</mi><mi>r</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>c</mi><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108803_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>r</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>)</mo></math>가 성립합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108804_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;예를 들어,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 다음 그림에서 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>가", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108806_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>의 내접원이고", "type": 0}, {"text": " 세 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>D</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>E</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>F</mi></math>는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 접점입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi><mo>,</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108810_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi><mo>,</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108811_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi></math>일 때,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108812_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>x</mi></math>의 값을 구해봅시다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108813_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>가", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>의 접선이므로", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi></math>이라 하면,", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>12</mn><mo>-</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi><mo>,</mo></math>", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>F</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo></math><math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>-</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi></math>입니다.", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3621}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>이므로", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>10</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>-</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>12</mn><mo>-</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>,</mo></math>", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>,</mo></math>", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn></math>입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br> 한편, 다음 그림과 같이", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108823_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>가 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>90</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>인", "type": 0}, {"text": " 직각삼각형 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>에 내접하고", "type": 0}, {"text": " 두 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>D</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>E</mi></math>가 접점이면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108826_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108827_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>D</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>E</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>90</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108828_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9633;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>D</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>E</mi></math>는", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108829_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 한 변의 길이가 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>r</mi></math>인", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108830_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 정사각형입니다.", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3622}}, {"text": " 따라서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108832_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mi>r</mi></math>이", "type": 0}, {"text": " 성립합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108834_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "[문단 나누기]", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>원에 외접하는 사각형에는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 어떤 성질이 있을까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;원에 외접하는 사각형은", "type": 0}, {"text": " 두 쌍의 대변의 길이의", "type": 0}, {"text": " 합이 같고,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 두 쌍의 대변의 길이의", "type": 0}, {"text": " 합이 같은 사각형은", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원에 외접합니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;이 성질을", "type": 0}, {"text": " 수학적으로 설명해 봅시다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br> 다음 그림과 같이", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108846_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>가", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108847_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9633;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>D</mi></math>의 내접원이고,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 네 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>P</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>Q</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>R</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>S</mi></math>가", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108849_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 그 접점일 때,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 접선의 성질에 의해", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>S</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>,</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108852_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>Q</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>,</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108853_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>Q</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>R</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>,</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108854_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>R</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>S</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108855_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108856_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>R</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>R</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108857_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>S</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>Q</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>Q</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>S</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108858_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>S</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>S</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>Q</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>Q</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>가 성립합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108860_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 따라서", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원에 외접하는 사각형의", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108862_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 두 쌍의 대변의 길이의 합은", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108863_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 서로 같습니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108864_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<br> 반대로 두 쌍의", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108865_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 대변의 길이의 합이", "type": 0}, {"text": " 서로 같은 사각형은", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원에 외접하는 사각형입니다.", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3623}}, {"text": " 예를 들어,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 정사각형, 마름모는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 두 대변의 길이의 합이", "type": 0}, {"text": " 서로 같으므로", "type": 0}, {"text": " 항상 원에 외접합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108873_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;예를 들어,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 다음 그림에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108875_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>가", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108876_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 직사각형 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>D</mi></math>에 내접하고", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></math>일 때,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108878_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>의 길이를 구해봅시다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108879_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br> <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi></math>라고 하면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/108880_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn></math>입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": " 직각삼각형 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi><mi>C</mi></math>에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><msqrt><msup><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><msup><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><msqrt><mn>16</mn></msqrt><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>4</mn></math>이고,", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9633;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>D</mi></math>가 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>에 외접하므로", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>,", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3624}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>4</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>,</mo></math>", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn><mo>,</mo></math>", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></math>입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": " 따라서 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>의 길이는", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>6</mn></math>입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "[문단 나누기]", "type": 0}]', NULL, NULL, '2024-02-15 09:58:33', '2024-02-15 09:58:33'),
	(246, 736, '[{"text": "원주각이란 무엇이며", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원주각에는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 어떤 성질이 있을까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;다음 그림과 같이", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109109_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 호 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></math> 위에 있지 않은", "type": 0}, {"text": " 한 점을 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>P</mi></math>라고 했을 때", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109111_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi></math>를", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109112_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 호 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></math>에 대한", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109113_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 원주각이라고 하고,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109114_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 호 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></math>를", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원주각 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi></math>에 대한", "type": 0}, {"text": " 호라고 합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109117_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;이때,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109119_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 호 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></math>가 정해지면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109120_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 중심각 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>O</mi><mi>B</mi></math>는", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109121_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 하나로 정해지지만,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원주각 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi></math>는", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109123_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 다음 그림과 같이", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109124_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>P</mi></math>의 위치에 따라", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109125_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 무수히 많이 정할 수 있습니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109126_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;이때,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 한 원에서", "type": 0}, {"text": " 한 호에 대한", "type": 0}, {"text": " 원주각의 크기는", "type": 0}, {"text": " 점 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>P</mi></math>의 위치에 관계없이", "type": 0}, {"text": " 그 호에 대한", "type": 0}, {"text": " 중심각의 크기의 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>입니다,", "type": 0}, {"text": " 즉,", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>O</mi><mi>B</mi></math>입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;이와 같은 성질이", "type": 0}, {"text": " 항상 성립하는지 알아봅시다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;원의 중심 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>의 위치를", "type": 0}, {"text": " 세 가지 경우", "type": 0}, {"text": "(중심 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>가", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109140_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 원주각 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi></math>의", "type": 0}, {"text": " 한 변 위에,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109142_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 내부에,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109143_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 외부에 있는 경우)로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109144_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 나누어 생각해 봅시다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109145_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;(1) 중심 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>가", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi></math>의", "type": 0}, {"text": " 한 변 위에 있는 경우에", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>O</mi><mi>B</mi></math>입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br> 다음 그림에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109150_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi></math>는", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109151_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>인 이등변삼각형이므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109152_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109153_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 이때", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>O</mi><mi>B</mi></math>는", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109155_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi></math>의 한 외각이므로", "type": 2, "question": {"id": 3625}}, {"text": " 삼각형의 외각의 성질에 의해", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>O</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109158_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>A</mi><mo>+</mo><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>O</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109159_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>2</mn><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109160_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " 따라서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109161_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo></math>", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109162_training_1.jpg", "last": "0"}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>O</mi><mi>B</mi></math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "/data/math/training_img/109163_training_1.jpg", "last": "1"}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;(2) 중심 <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mi>O</mi></math>가", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>B</mi></math>의", "type": 0}, {"text": " 내부에 있는 경우에", "type": 0}, {"text": " <math xmlns=\\