<mn>3</mn>&#160;</mrow> <mrow>&#160; <mn>6</mn> <mo>&#215;</mo> <mn>3</mn>&#160;</mrow>&#160;</mfrac> <mo>=</mo> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>15</mn> <mn>18</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>이고", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/ZINrVoQh6p55QDVJzNkeXhPftOJ8CZTj24QtuuCv.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>8</mn> <mn>9</mn>&#160;</mfrac> <mo>=</mo> <mfrac>&#160; <mrow>&#160; <mn>8</mn> <mo>&#215;</mo> <mn>2</mn>&#160;</mrow> <mrow>&#160; <mn>9</mn> <mo>&#215;</mo> <mn>2</mn>&#160;</mrow>&#160;</mfrac> <mo>=</mo> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>16</mn> <mn>18</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/O1xu1vtIdD7Zz9Ln38zpJtKCn3AXY4saYpvCn8so.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;따라서&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mfenced>&#160;<mrow>&#160;<mfrac>&#160;<mn>5</mn> <mn>6</mn>&#160;</mfrac> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>,</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mfrac>&#160;<mn>8</mn> <mn>9</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</mrow>&#160;</mfenced>&#160;</math>을 최소공배수로 통분하면", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mfenced>&#160;<mrow>&#160;<mfrac>&#160;<mn>15</mn> <mn>18</mn>&#160;</mfrac> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>,</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mfrac>&#160;<mn>16</mn> <mn>18</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</mrow>&#160;</mfenced>&#160;</math>이 됩니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/K6YnJc3gtnLFH15ikXYVYVbIUFWVLsfsCbHxge2G.png", "last": true}}]', '{"questions": [{"id": 9666}]}', '{"questions": [{"id": 11652}, {"id": 11653}]}', '2024-04-01 07:33:17', '2024-04-18 05:14:47'),
	(430, 235, '[{"text": "분모가 다른 분수의 크기를 비교해 볼까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>5</mn> <mn>9</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>와&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>7</mn> <mn>9</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>과 같이 분모가 같은 분수는", "type": 0}, {"text": "분자가 크면 더 크므로", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>9</mn></mfrac><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#60;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mfrac><mn>7</mn><mn>9</mn></mfrac></math>입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "그렇다면&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>5</mn> <mn>8</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>와&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>7</mn> <mn>12</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>과 같이 분모가 다른 분수의 크기 비교는 어떻게 할까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;분모가 다른 두 분수는 통분하여 분모를 같게 한 후", "type": 0}, {"text": "분자의 크기를 비교합니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>5</mn> <mn>8</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>와&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>7</mn> <mn>12</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>의 크기를 비교하기 위해 분모를 통분하면", "type": 0}, {"text": "두 분모&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>8</mn>&#160;</math>과&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>12</mn>&#160;</math>의 최소공배수가&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>24</mn>&#160;</math>이므로", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9546}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>24</mn>&#160;</math>를 공통분모로 해서 통분합니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>5</mn> <mn>8</mn>&#160;</mfrac> <mo>=</mo> <mfrac>&#160; <mrow>&#160; <mn>5</mn> <mo>&#215;