}, {"text": "나누어서 계산해 봅니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>2</mn> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>1</mn> <mn>4</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>&#215;</mo>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>1</mn> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>3</mn> <mn>5</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>을 계산 시", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}}, {"text": "대분수&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>1</mn> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>3</mn> <mn>5</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>을 자연수&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>1</mn>&#160;</math>과 진분수&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>3</mn> <mn>5</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>으로 나누어", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9902}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>2</mn> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>1</mn> <mn>4</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>과 각각 곱하면", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>2</mn> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>1</mn> <mn>4</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>&#215;</mo>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>1</mn> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>3</mn> <mn>5</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math><math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>=</mo>&#160;</math><math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#215;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>+</mo>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#215;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math>", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>=</mo>&#160;</math><math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>2</mn> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>1</mn> <mn>4</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>+</mo>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mfenced><mrow><mfrac><mn>9</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#215;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math>", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>=</mo>&#160;</math><math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>2</mn> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>1</mn> <mn>4</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>+</mo>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>27</mn> <mn>20</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>=</mo>&#160;</math><math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>2</mn> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>5</mn> <mn>20</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>+</mo>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>1</mn> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>7</mn> <mn>20</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>=</mo>&#160;</math><math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>3</mn> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>12</mn> <mn>20</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>=</mo>&#160;</math><math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>3</mn> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>3</mn> <mn>5</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>이 계산됩니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "[문단 나누기]", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mi>&#51088;&#50672;&#49688;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#215;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>&#48516;&#49688;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo></math>,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mi>&#48516;&#49688;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#215;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>&#51088;&#50672;&#49688;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo></math>에서", "type": 0}, {"text": "자연수를 분수 형태인&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mstyle mathsize=\\"16px\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mrow>&#160; <mo>(</mo> <mi>&#51088;&#50672;&#49688;</mi> <mo>)</mo>&#160;</mrow> <mn>1</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</mstyle>&#160;</math>&nbsp;로 나타내면", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mi>&#51088;&#50672;&#49688;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#215;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>&#48516;&#49688;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo></math>,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mi>&#48516;&#49688;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#215;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>&#51088;&#50672;&#49688;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo></math>의 계산도", "type": 0}, {"text": "분자는 분자끼리, 분모는 분모끼리 곱하여 계산할 수 있습니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;예를 들어&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>3</mn>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>&#215;</mo>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>5</mn> <mn>9</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>를 계산해 봅니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/cZVyRohA2XFpZJ2cFYCpaInqfS8AaM659U5x45AO.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>3</mn>&#160;</math><math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>=</mo>&#160;</math><math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>3</mn> <mn>1</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>과 같으므로", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9903}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>3</mn>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>&#215;</mo>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>5</mn> <mn>9</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>는&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>3</mn> <mn>1</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mo>&#215;</mo>&#160;</math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>5</mn> <mn>9</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>로 바꿀 수 있습니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/0geOyukHxuZrQM8YVv7PXR0kHtrOCVpvfKVWRXAk.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "이를 분자, 분모의 공약수&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>3</mn>&#160;</math>으로 약분하면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/nM3cfPG46niaD6MjAvHqAy8nfawfzyzVVwZuiSSu.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mfrac>&#160; <mn>5</mn> <mn>3</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>가 되고", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/kmlnEn4jDXiHX4TyNBRvPcOEsrV8Jg2XM3kZeabY.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "이를 대분수로 바꾸면", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160; <mn>1</mn> <mfrac>&#160; <mn>2</mn> <mn>3</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>가 계산됩니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/o4z28Egp5smX5Z9N2FPirYK4SjNfN7JT7WvLG31Q.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;요약하면,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mi>&#48516;&#49688;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#215;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>&#51088;&#50672;&#49688;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo></math>,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mi>&#51088;&#50672;&#49688;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#215;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>&#48516;&#49688;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo></math>,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>(</mo><mi>&#48516;&#49688;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#215;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>&#48516;&#49688;</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo></math>&nbsp;등 분수의 곱셈은 모두", "type": 0}, {"text": "분자는 분자끼리, 분모는 분모끼리 곱하여 계산하면 됩니다.", "type": 0}]', '{"questions": [{"id": 9740}]}', '{"questions": [{"id": 11840}, {"id": 11841}]}', '2024-04-03 05:03:34', '2024-04-19 01:55:14'),
	(460, 268, '[{"text": "도형의 합동을 알아볼까요?", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/mNFbNVZpVbfTyB08u9T36V2E29qS7MNMbhYFyTCX.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;주어진 그림에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/g55hXAY4TX8Z0nYvSkeO2s7Ao5pucaiEE23Nm8zu.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "도형 &lsquo;가&rsquo;와 완전히 겹쳐지는 도형은", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/J3zuscCgbRfIbN9TV2KDvaUaCkAtgZV9MeQlIf4y.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "도형 &lsquo;바&rsquo;이고,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/6Zg0r5pFDOI84AkzbqVSyr01CEBynzSvzyXQvNxn.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "도형 &lsquo;나&rsquo;와 완전히 겹쳐지는 도형은", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/2Z5yNSDDSXiBf1gF0CwoS0BpxKY0tvRfycdGbfhH.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "도형 &lsquo;사&rsquo;입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/y5eTxIiIztLrHtPRuopfR0x31M1tLlYsEdIAcPi7.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;이와 같이 모양과 크기가 같아서 포개었을 때,", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9905}}, {"text": "완전히 겹치는 두 도형을", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9913}}, {"text": "서로 합동이라고 합니다.", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/xw62ohiJPC3SMI8IPDUOvbV1vm5T5jBZiV5em2vm.png", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 10117}}, {"text": "이때 도형을 뒤집거나 돌려서 포개었을 때", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9914}}, {"text": "완전히 겹치는 두 도형은 합동이고,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/EXkfqNggzWk65usB0ndrh6pBBj4UaFCVR1VowDds.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "모양은 같지만 크기가 다른 두 도형은", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/3AKfi09RD2c5t1QUtp3m14haliICz5LKD6fUeglD.png", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9904}}, {"text": "합동이 아닙니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/rdiE6L22riZLKBWPmdmc3hOoLduOlg9UXiZyLXQc.png", "last": true}}]', '{"questions": [{"id": 9741}]}', '{"questions": [{"id": 11842}, {"id": 11843}]}', '2024-04-03 05:07:39', '2024-04-19 02:08:52'),
	(461, 268, '[{"text": "합동인 도형의 성질을 알아볼까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;서로 합동인 두 도형을 완전히 포개었을 때,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/Z0Qy55134AM3Xi1VaEDwKqutRTS9z2vyUzel9F5D.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "겹치는 점을 대응점,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/C7UxSt5SIUky03I9msC84CjjibhsB5BRsgPE3uFr.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "겹치는 변을 대응변,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/a9GyNfAVZ4jM7fXV1nPt0Mk9MVSTvIUuFuxUMYrk.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "겹치는 각을 대응각이라고 합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/AmWWxoJA4ZckxIuexgDxuFSDq7pPEWAc8KC7xxHZ.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "서로 합동인 두 삼각형에는", "type": 0}, {"text": "대응점, 대응변, 대응각이 각각 3쌍,", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9910}}, {"text": "서로 합동인 두 사각형에는", "type": 0}, {"text": "각각 4쌍 있습니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/k9zQqxNUCRIQx3MzqmHo6v4rA11rApoNgOA1Tyb1.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;합동인 두 도형의 성질을 살펴보면,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/wGUtmykelJDtdCaHjYtIQ9x5TFgpTN7iMvZnoCxV.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "서로 합동인 두 도형은", "type": 0}, {"text": "각각의 대응변의 길이와 대응각의 크기가", "type": 0}, {"text": "서로 같습니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/If43W6J3UBTSV6wINSx6yvnSgSaM1Rui6JFnvlxc.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;예를 들어 주어진 그림에서", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/SB1BMub6qiBfjBPxEF3zCDZS8CGY5BDuZXeLavRH.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "사각형 ㄱㄴㄷㄹ과 사각형 ㅁㅂㅅㅇ이 합동이면,", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9912}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;－ 대응변의 길이는 서로 같으므로", "type": 0}, {"text": "(변 ㄱㄴ) ＝ (변 ㅁㅂ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/pgnfiFPc0VH984OZI8V88CR1P7O4HG0cEaYwGwAW.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(변 ㄴㄷ) ＝ (변 ㅂㅅ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/iWuRu3A7H6J1EBeuzdfPsXtlFBMIwpRCF3SMZRXa.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(변 ㄷㄹ) ＝ (변 ㅅㅇ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/BXk3QT1biJZTDFWKTm5JFABhdQlb7wUC4tO5uo0o.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(변 ㄹㄱ) ＝ (변 ㅇㅁ)입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/iSokwV3DLGAvcUPVrpHAoGVyPp8npg4PMGbOmr1u.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;－ 대응각의 크기는 서로 같으므로", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9909}}, {"text": "(각 ㄱㄴㄷ) ＝ (각 ㅁㅂㅅ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/8fj32PfC6a1qqb5h0gxpb20KRro2n8ZBXFODorp8.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(각 ㄴㄷㄹ) ＝ (각 ㅂㅅㅇ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/lVGB7EKRxctKtQI67M3S9idDyRV5WjOG00XVreFo.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(각 ㄷㄹㄱ) ＝ (각 ㅅㅇㅁ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/j0qUcOQZ8Os4hDwjyechHqfV2lpFW7c6JFQ3M02E.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(각 ㄹㄱㄴ) ＝ (각 ㅇㅁㅂ)입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/QSdRrXYSaDzefEpxN4yX68vWNzPg0LWIFww6qwkP.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "[문단 나누기]", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;직사각형을 잘라서 서로 합동인 도형 2개와", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/R0Kwe0mLXEMymooIzMBqtqLbMvHAHQZtlgq75SXU.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "4개를 만들어 봅니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/uYT44TuUG9C5by0LhZFCHXWJttkMMUi0Zkof8Hw1.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "점선을 따라 자른 도형들을 포개었을 때", "type": 0}, {"text": "완전히 겹치도록 만듭니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/80ShIk9kjKm02N783DXiFzqvKsGPKcN1HqFXwr23.png", "last": true}}]', '{"questions": [{"id": 9742}]}', '{"questions": [{"id": 11844}, {"id": 11845}]}', '2024-04-03 05:07:40', '2024-04-19 02:10:22'),
	(462, 271, '[{"text": "선대칭도형을 알아볼까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;한 직선을 따라 접어서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/UqxDUgLYwzKvY3JmvfdK29lSv4W8CtBQL6Wdjk6g.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "완전히 겹치는 도형을", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/uxB3Rue30DH6SFCwpKts7RO8nls7U8Az3noj6q7q.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "선대칭도형이라고 하고,", "type": 0}, {"text": "이때 그 직선을 대칭축이라고 합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/XMckTg5X9EcyjLzCZttMXISriMUbZhwvo4R8ey42.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "대칭축을 따라 포개었을 때", "type": 0}, {"text": "겹치는 점을 대응점,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/PbuTdpB6y0axejBGOyeZdlhlXj0eZkEhiwAkpToJ.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "겹치는 변을 대응변,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/S43s2HW3gOkv91C9JWsGh0gzwxHpEN0E5moejqiv.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "겹치는 각을 대응각이라고 합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/viPZG8YWd2dHzHGmkRBBpdFxCKwcuMxxbSR7ajX7.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;선대칭도형의 성질을 알아봅니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/BX2npjzTt50Vb7y2P98jz7UhPR4gAFNWE7do9Ihs.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;● 선대칭도형에서 대칭축을 중심으로 접었을 때", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9936}}, {"text": "왼쪽 도형과 오른쪽 도형은 합동입니다.", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9937}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;● 대응변의 길이는 각각 같습니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;(변 ㄱㅅ) ＝ (변 ㅂㅅ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/sxJOKO5HGoqHb9FFwRm624vqvvTYNOEtSjqdF3Rn.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(변 ㄱㄴ) ＝ (변 ㅂㅁ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/nxMtIz44MonyltiwE6rNeux4YjQQKw3pekOliBsL.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(변 ㄴㄷ) ＝ (변 ㅁㄹ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/sLQzkv54FBYJ4idTnj5O0js9gGad6eeRXb2KhIfK.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(변 ㄷㅈ) ＝ (변 ㄹㅈ)", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/GUGQ5iDr5JsZ1MsfmqoDolGpsko0GR7IhEhv2PS3.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;● 대응각의 크기는 각각 같습니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;(각 ㄱㄴㄷ) ＝ (각 ㅂㅁㄹ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/qMJEByikHrPibK8RGisuUY7hidhrvNc7GUqSwn27.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(각 ㄴㄷㅈ) ＝ (각 ㅁㄹㅈ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/G06gUTPEmCPNCdz78LzCAb8Otz1aEtnd1cqN2nI2.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(각 ㅅㄱㄴ) ＝ (각 ㅅㅂㅁ)", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/sR2eiB4AbyM0vw8o3ekKpnPE8ok2WQ7ADWnxYmCi.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;● 대응점을 이은 선분은", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/DZoAIYBfyvzC72aYQtqC3O829BU7DMZaNfGCj6tx.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "대칭축과", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/DFt8w7q8EnbUDgj1LxnHACL0bkt6JCAiWO4ziP7m.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "수직으로 만납니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/CX1qqCC1jhzm4eFMEgEGeCSD4JtfJShGH4oAj76k.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "선분 ㄴㅁ이 대칭축과 만나서 이루는 각은", "type": 0}, {"text": "90<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#176;</mo></math>입니다.", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9934}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;● 대칭축은 대응점을 이은 선분을 이등분하므로", "type": 0}, {"text": "각각의 대응점에서 대칭축까지의 거리는 같습니다.", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9935}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;(선분 ㄱㅅ) ＝ (선분 ㅂㅅ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/t8ybf93vZqLy8iIt9fcTwMjdfOr33KcHEVBNbGxz.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(선분 ㄴㅇ) ＝ (선분 ㅁㅇ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/yOM84tBFfhSLj28aaPbaXxMSDaeqi9r2JykEJopj.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(선분 ㄷㅈ) ＝ (선분 ㄹㅈ)", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/gMP7jeJ04gvCGIi5R1e9Z3xQOcw87s4TTXpF6cIQ.png", "last": false}}]', '{"questions": [{"id": 9743}]}', '{"questions": [{"id": 11846}, {"id": 11847}]}', '2024-04-03 05:09:26', '2024-04-19 02:21:03'),
	(463, 271, '[{"text": "선대칭도형을 그려볼까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;선대칭도형을 그릴 때에는", "type": 0}, {"text": "먼저 선대칭도형의 대칭축을 중심으로", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9943}}, {"text": "각 점의 대응점을 찾아 표시한 후,", "type": 0}, {"text": "대응점을 차례로 이어 선대칭도형을 완성합니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "선대칭도형이 되도록 주어진 그림을 완성해 봅니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/IR4eULtQs3kCp2j6n84g0uhB7SUqXN9nFIzGOzZ3.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;① 점 ㄴ에서 대칭축 ㅁㅂ을 지나는 수선을 긋고,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/yrYj1ZMb5LLKbAYgboSt4NF4ss79yfgf41hBVjYn.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "대칭축과 만나는 점을 점 ㅅ이라고 합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/sxUw96MyXz4hpcTPYkEUTOz5nhGHgdn0eSg9Lz3X.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;② 이 수선에 선분 ㄴㅅ의 길이와 같도록", "type": 0}, {"text": "점 ㄴ의 대응점 ㅇ을 찍고,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/2yobpsP3DMfRstB8kKw4MvbGnpITgLM3o3tazaA5.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "같은 방법으로 (선분 ㄷㄹ) ＝ (선분 ㄹㅈ)이 되도록", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/9iem50wObbGXfyzfzAltcFLEgfrWsr40nI6yTEqi.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "점 ㄷ의 대응점 ㅈ을 찍습니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/5TQL3py7m5E4t3vbRwwpApDbL6qfE8NHJo8hm4fX.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;③ 점 ㄱ, 점 ㅇ, 점 ㅈ, 점 ㄹ을 연결하여", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/rgPx45RrHgovykPnf8NN46wBfYLHaUMx53EsxoU4.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "선대칭도형을 완성합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/SMS6GG4iTBSIUHsXEBCpY0sxvXH3iI5hgcRNp0CO.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;선대칭도형에서 대칭축은", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/S8yoviLzCqqxKXV13uCRy0t9MsnW0BXeROuwHUza.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "선대칭도형의 모양에 따라 1개일 수도 있고", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9945}}, {"text": "여러 개일 수도 있습니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "대칭축이 여러 개일 때", "type": 0}, {"text": "모든 대칭축은 한 점에서 만납니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/hSSHLBykLc4BvHD4OzfXv0JZBHQ6qFBJorJjjhwV.png", "last": true}}]', '{"questions": [{"id": 9744}]}', '{"questions": [{"id": 11870}, {"id": 11871}]}', '2024-04-03 05:09:29', '2024-04-19 02:46:27'),
	(464, 274, '[{"text": "점대칭도형과 그 성질을 알아볼까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;정삼각형은 점 ㅇ을 중심으로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/WGDirLg9IzhBw4mbIhqcNdiCzFlPB4egd6mlkbGm.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "180<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#176;</mo></math>&nbsp;돌리면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/YHnuJTuiXLvCL0XlaXYqsRb5yODHDEQDA0GoRs2c.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "겹쳐지지 않고,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/sfImTbHWyxqHfbCezeu5Sch7pjBgxl9bZ5l6ZxMX.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "정육각형은 점 ㅇ을 중심으로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/OoDiVarDMdeOcpX7euIkkG4WChOskDLoyh2NQZt8.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "180<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#176;</mo></math> 돌리면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/HDF68CZ6uAA7lPDCbBQeEgpkVLHLIUVZ56a7VMMH.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "완전히 겹쳐집니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/uXqZerWCPcPHrrAfJ7fD5bBCVzZ4ww0uoUh66erk.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;이와 같이 한 도형을 어떤 점을 중심으로 180<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#176;</mo></math>&nbsp;돌렸을 때", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/6uNEpfoDU19k8XWi74voA5DcLk9erJe4Z5vuy3sn.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "처음 도형과 완전히 겹치면", "type": 0}, {"text": "이 도형을 점대칭도형이라고 하고,", "type": 0}, {"text": "이때 그 점을", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/Rjvm7kxgjIrZXildqo0Zn1SkZgB1iGHsiGyF3Yhw.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "대칭의 중심이라고 합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/2jHpmx2luDoAKSphMyCFAnlAW25Il2HO5FilagnI.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "점대칭도형에서 대칭의 중심은 항상 1개입니다.", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9955}}, {"text": "대칭의 중심을 중심으로 180<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#176;</mo></math> 돌렸을 때", "type": 0}, {"text": "겹치는 점을 대응점,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/f39L9dQm6cI0OzAY6qHOCqX3UkCaAu7z5aF2sqMF.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "겹치는 변을 대응변,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/J8INS9SGkYDDjxwSngy8TqdVCPWFy7mjDDxYTBBE.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "겹치는 각을 대응각이라고 합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/QEAZHeuBnwOGLJYifxKNYnQqpkmQUwL6ThKTJCKM.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;점대칭도형의 성질을 알아봅니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/tBQipyVfZLloDHNXufa8VBDkwAC039svnNzzxMTR.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;● 대응변의 길이는 각각 같습니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "(변 ㄱㄴ) ＝ (변 ㄷㄹ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/sQef4QJMelS8nsxUXdXN2sQaIa422JuVQh7Rytol.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(변 ㄴㄷ) ＝ (변 ㄹㄱ)", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/VS513AZXp4dmjOk9goFxw9kBMcVtSQ6Uk4cFrLNo.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;● 대응각의 크기는 각각 같습니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "(각 ㄱㄴㄷ) ＝ (각 ㄷㄹㄱ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/v38udUUbMbq51MIB2ehIgttha3kvXYYQT4YoKci8.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(각 ㄴㄷㄹ) ＝ (각 ㄹㄱㄴ)", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/qpRAxuGRBN2YhDXJ91yVdo9M9uB06YnwxrB3UBf3.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;● 대칭의 중심은 대응점을 이은 선분을 이등분하므로", "type": 0}, {"text": "각각의 대응점에서 대칭의 중심까지의 거리는 같습니다.", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9956}}, {"text": "(선분 ㄱㅇ) ＝ (선분 ㄷㅇ),", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/F17VPP2DMKlEOgK4QNCVQuXYvuUyUwaHhKSzIIpL.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "(선분 ㄴㅇ) ＝ (선분 ㄹㅇ)", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/7zFaQFHFm8pD8ST65HIWjfrw8kMf293oYmFZEymo.png", "last": false}}]', '{"questions": [{"id": 9747}]}', '{"questions": [{"id": 11872}, {"id": 11873}]}', '2024-04-03 05:12:48', '2024-04-19 02:54:30'),
	(465, 274, '[{"text": "점대칭도형을 그려볼까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;점대칭도형을 그릴 때에는", "type": 0}, {"text": "먼저 각 점에서 대칭의 중심을 지나는 직선을 긋고", "type": 0}, {"text": "각 점에서 대칭의 중심까지의 길이와 같도록", "type": 0}, {"text": "대응점을 찾아 표시한 후,", "type": 0}, {"text": "대응점을 차례로 이어 점대칭도형을 완성합니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "점대칭도형이 되도록 주어진 그림을 완성해 봅니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/9ZAfDQgdcoohh66QR0OIAo6fuqmQWOCVqVdj9PcW.png", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9959}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;① 점 ㄴ에서", "type": 0}, {"text": "대칭의 중심인 점 ㅇ을 지나는 직선을 긋습니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/bCUBVuUlBpEBIl66FNahl9hocgmIpZJURad5m302.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "이 직선에 선분 ㄴㅇ과 길이가 같은 선분 ㅂㅇ이 되도록", "type": 0}, {"text": "점 ㄴ의 대응점을 찾아", "type": 0}, {"text": "점 ㅂ으로 표시합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/mORPeJJDDb17VqfulAqWxUrPwL3i7e7mvhnTpfUc.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;② 점 ㄷ에서", "type": 0}, {"text": "대칭의 중심인 점 ㅇ을 지나는 직선을 긋습니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/HRwvWYt2l01dEq4LJoipL1kEjPRC4ZuYHce2UL5V.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "이 직선에 선분 ㄷㅇ과 길이가 같은 선분 ㅅㅇ이 되도록", "type": 0}, {"text": "점 ㄷ의 대응점을 찾아", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9967}}, {"text": "점 ㅅ으로 표시합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/1X7g05gUtHo45TRQMvxS2A1lLelzx02nltuH8nQu.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;③ 점 ㄹ에서", "type": 0}, {"text": "대칭의 중심인 점 ㅇ을 지나는 직선을 긋습니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/jtMsCx1OOMF6rNqkhWT4qkWqkx8ONvEyJriKOTAK.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "이 직선에 선분 ㄹㅇ과 길이가 같은 선분 ㅈㅇ이 되도록", "type": 0}, {"text": "점 ㄹ의 대응점을 찾아", "type": 0}, {"text": "점 ㅈ으로 표시합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/6sJa51o1S2xAU91l2f8QvV5yctdu5ybS1Oc49ces.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;④ 점 ㄱ의 대응점은 점 ㅁ입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/sVnpROJdvMacmSRCexHiDPuxYN3bmACnmepOQY8v.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "점 ㅁ과 점 ㅂ,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/DUkQf7KZqkGKk7nAaXJuMcESa4EZiNNROarfnWNp.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "점 ㅂ과 점 ㅅ,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/tufKxuqjFO9R8ICcpsvx8ZhE3W3P5bwtSMc09iF4.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "점 ㅅ과 점 ㅈ,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/rh5uOqJeVdGroA7jwbKQlA41uSn2PCsRG445iuWK.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "점 ㅈ과 점 ㄱ을 차례로 이어", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/qTcEX1eOjkE0CMQjPLVQw2m8nwSsBJvq1zFLEbv9.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "점대칭도형이 되도록 그립니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/De6WlsrtoBALwfy1NhB1oKjfSXkCxCntTPML1XCA.png", "last": true}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;점대칭도형인 사각형을 알아봅니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "정사각형,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/7JMW4BwX9sPbUD1sftUdfI1kn4GWPPjKg9OT6DNm.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "직사각형,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/bLyEtpCXxBCceukJMwPiRL0u4SAdfNddI0nf3mu7.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "마름모,", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/jySg1XQ46MTtT2UsslegNOW1Ra0M6i5Fznpap6vd.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "평행사변형은", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/XrXEo3Jc2KXs3r51kVf24owSy6rpcb2PE9oKJKh5.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "모두 점대칭도형입니다.", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9965}}, {"text": "특히, 정사각형, 직사각형, 마름모는", "type": 0}, {"text": "선대칭도형이기도 합니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/xeZCcOiJCBkWz7Hl2bulXDzKnIhrAK7R8M1aIrnt.png", "last": true}}]', '{"questions": [{"id": 9748}]}', '{"questions": [{"id": 11874}, {"id": 11875}]}', '2024-04-03 05:12:53', '2024-04-19 03:04:00'),
	(466, 277, '[{"text": "(<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>1</mn></math>보다 작은 소수)&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#215;</mo></math>&nbsp;(자연수)를 알아볼까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#215;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mn>4</mn></math>와 같은 (<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>1</mn></math>보다 작은 소수)&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#215;</mo></math>&nbsp;(자연수)는", "type": 0}, {"text": "여러 가지 방법으로 계산할 수 있습니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;첫 번째, 덧셈식으로 계산하는 방법입니다.", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/ZPpyEbtMteSqO4Oxf2GkpEMM3WAzle9ViIgKu5ab.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#215;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mn>4</mn></math>는", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/irZIbfumV7T6MwyG11zQLnOUBK089hluWLTdXs7Y.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>4</mn></math>를", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/CmaXPGaP9V3zSkL6ttNFrChWsTZJZloM4ZEVytUg.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>4</mn></math>번 더하면 되므로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/y8i7L9uQLW12Du5SEdmQAhsmMUdknh0Z9Ke2pN2V.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>=</mo