	(471, 280, '[{"text": "(<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>1</mn>&#160;</math>보다 큰 소수)&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mo>&#215;</mo>&#160;</math>&nbsp;(<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>1</mn>&#160;</math>보다 큰 소수)를 알아볼까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>1</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>6</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#215;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mn>2</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>3</mn>&#160;</math>과 같은 (<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>1</mn>&#160;</math>보다 큰 소수)&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mo>&#215;</mo></math>&nbsp;(<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>1</mn>&#160;</math>보다 큰 소수)는", "type": 0}, {"text": "소수를 분수로 나타내어 분수의 곱셈으로 계산하거나", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 10009}}, {"text": "자연수의 곱셈을 이용하여 계산할 수 있습니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;첫 번째, 분수의 곱셈으로 계산하는 방법입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>1</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>6</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#215;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mn>2</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>3</mn>&#160;</math>의 계산에서", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>1</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>6</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>=</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mfrac>&#160;<mn>16</mn> <mn>10</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>이고&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>2</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>3</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>=</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mfrac>&#160;<mn>23</mn> <mn>10</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>이므로", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>1</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>6</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#215;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mn>2</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>3</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>=</mo>&#160;</math>", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#