	(494, 313, '[{"text": "각 자리에서 나누어떨어지지 않는&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mo>(</mo> <mi>&#49548;&#49688;</mi> <mo>)</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#247;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>(</mo> <mi>&#51088;&#50672;&#49688;</mi> <mo>)</mo>&#160;</math>는 어떻게 계산할까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>22</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>5</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#247;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mn>3</mn>&#160;</math>과 같이", "type": 0}, {"text": "각 자리에서 나누어떨어지지 않는&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mo>(</mo> <mi>&#49548;&#49688;</mi> <mo>)</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#247;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>(</mo> <mi>&#51088;&#50672;&#49688;</mi> <mo>)</mo>&#160;</math>는", "type": 0}, {"text": "세 가지 방법을 이용해 계산할 수 있습니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;첫 번째, 분수의 나눗셈으로 바꾸어 계산하는 방법입니다.", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>22</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>5</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#247;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mn>3</mn>&#160;</math>의 계산에서", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>22</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>5</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>=</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mfrac>&#160;<mn>225</mn> <mn>10</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>이므로", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 10221}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>22</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>5</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#247;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mn>3</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>=</mo>&#160;</math>", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mfrac>&#160;<mn>225</mn> <mn>10</mn>&#160;</mfrac> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#247;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mn>3</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>=</mo>&#160;</math><math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mfrac><mrow><mn>225</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#247;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mn>10</mn></mfrac><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>=</mo></math>