	(497, 316, '[{"text": "몫의 소수 첫째 자리에&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>0</mn></math>이 있는&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mo>(</mo> <mi>&#49548;&#49688;</mi> <mo>)</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#247;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>(</mo> <mi>&#51088;&#50672;&#49688;</mi> <mo>)</mo>&#160;</math>는 어떻게 계산할까요?", "type": 0}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp; <math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>6</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>24</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#247;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mn>6</mn>&#160;</math>과 같이", "type": 0}, {"text": "몫의 소수 첫째 자리에&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>0</mn></math>이 있는", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mo>(</mo> <mi>&#49548;&#49688;</mi> <mo>)</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#247;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>(</mo> <mi>&#51088;&#50672;&#49688;</mi> <mo>)</mo>&#160;</math>는", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}}, {"text": "세 가지 방법을 이용해 계산할 수 있습니다.", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;첫 번째, 분수의 나눗셈으로 바꾸어", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}}, {"text": "계산하는 방법입니다.", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>6</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>24</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#247;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mn>6</mn>&#160;</math>의 계산에서", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>6</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>24</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>=</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mfrac>&#160;<mn>624</mn> <mn>100</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>이므로", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mn>6</mn> <mo>.</mo> <mn>24</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#247;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mn>6</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>=</mo>&#160;</math>", "type": 0}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mfrac>&#160;<mn>624</mn> <mn>100</mn>&#160;</mfrac> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>&#247;</mo> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mn>6</mn> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>=</mo>&#160;</math><math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mfrac><mrow><mn>624</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#247;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow><mn>100</mn></mfrac><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>=</mo></math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mfrac>&#160;<mn>104</mn> <mn>100</mn>&#160;</mfrac> <mo>&#160;</mo> <mo>=</mo>&#160;</math><math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>04</mn></math>가 계산됩니다.", "type": 2, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}, "question": {"id": 9908}}, {"text": "<br>&nbsp;두 번째, 자연수의 나눗셈을 이용하여", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}}, {"text": "계산하는 방법입니다.", "type": 0, "image": {"src": "", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>624</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#247;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mn>104</mn></math>에서", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/8reZwx8pBFyu63sgNlJGWN4YQu4S1CKoYBhOpwBh.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "나누어지는 수&nbsp;<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>624</mn></math>가", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/92psJ54gg43xB4zq78GaVD9UlCNAhoNHb2RXPg9m.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\"><mn>6</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>24</mn></math>로", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/LY4XMqnDEGRfBzVkQGbFyifu6EDvJelQKNZ9Hj7y.png", "last": false}}, {"text": "<math xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\\">&#160;<mfrac>&#160;<mn>1</mn> <mn>100</mn>&#160;</mfrac>&#160;</math>배가 되면", "type": 1, "image": {"src": "https://dev-reading-math.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/temp/images/mCcrFETcmJ4grp7Df8uPl7jMwSD9NlCRoz4ALDii.png", "last": false}